data.description:
Come see this Beautiful Town home in Lakeside Landing Located in Irving. Minutes away from George Bush Turnpike. Nestled in a private and gated
quaint community. This two bedroom offers oversized Bedrooms, updated kitchen with New granite countertops. Plenty of cabinet space with soft close cabinets and drawers, hands free motion sensor faucet. Completed foundation repair as of 2023 with lifetime transferable warranty. New Insulation with 10 year warranty. Reserved Parking with one covered. Spacious patio deck with Waterfront view.    Refrigerator and Washer and Dryer will convey with the property.

Gate code 1212
Please close all blinds if you open them and do not adjust thermostat
